{"tid":2033991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港島衝突10人受傷　廁所女工被撞傷頭心臟病發命危","createTime":"2020-05-25T03:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T04:43:12.000Z","uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d6903d35f247354865946c32fbc56af6ebacb4b0","tid":2033991,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"今（24日）午發起「5.24反惡歌法大遊行」遊行，事件演變為警民衝突，多人在混亂中受傷。醫管局表示，截查晚上11時，共有10名傷者（30至72歲）分別被送往東區醫院、瑪麗醫院及律敦治醫院治理。其中1名女傷者，目前情況危殆；另外1男1女傷者情況穩定；剩餘5男2女則已經出院。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4547049/org/171e4a816fe296f04a46fa0312c2a9a9.jpg/AuXP3rJTulgxu2U64bUvEcwtVebA7djMBVDngy9Q54M?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4547049%2Forg%2F171e4a816fe296f04a46fa0312c2a9a9.jpg%2FAuXP3rJTulgxu2U64bUvEcwtVebA7djMBVDngy9Q54M%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=a0d5e97e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息指，該危殆女子是51歲南亞裔女子，任職公廁清潔工，事發時她在公廁內工作，突然有一班人衝入公廁內，惟不清楚該批人士的身份，混亂間女事主撞傷頭部。救護員其後到場，將她送往律敦治醫院搶救。據知，女事主患有心臟病。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AlQrk4lXmxs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAlQrk4lXmxs&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=dba26e12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AlQrk4lXmxs</a>"},{"pid":"25ced4279b1edbb4bd43b3cbfcdc5781a0e3ab51","tid":2033991,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"希望無事"},{"pid":"48a4d86903c065469a7130aae329bd1552fced98","tid":2033991,"uid":60297,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"李家超： 佢唔係現場出現就冇事， 去得嗰度就可能有呢啲風險"},{"pid":"e3351e0c07b75b5f288848b2ae2f1d714185f953","tid":2033991,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077e65c39c98e4cb0806c5b4b12e7ca81b9fb9d5","tid"